description: On a hot Orange County day, come on up to this super chic cart and cool yourself off the classy way with one of these refreshing, delicious, and creamy Celebrity Stars Pops. Their famously tasty flavors include Blueberry Pineapple, Chocolate Banana, Coconut, Strawberry Mojito, Strawberry Horchata, Lemon blueberry, Lemon pomegranate, Mango Cream, Watermelon, Arnold Palmer, and more daily creations too!Celebrity Stars Pops are vibrant, they’re scrumptious, they’re amazingly spectacular, and perfect for every type of party, so you just simply have to try them!
name: Celebrity Stars Pops
